# FastAPI URL Shortener

This is a simple project to create short URLs from long ones using FastAPI and SQLite.

## Features

- Make short links
- Set time limit for each link
- Use your own short code (optional)
- Get details of short links
- Logs requests and errors to external service

## Tools Used

- FastAPI
- SQLite (with SQLAlchemy)
- Pydantic
- ShortUUID

## API Endpoints

### POST /shorten

To create a short URL

**Request body:**
```json
{
  "url": "very-long-url-without-http-and-slashes",
  "validity_minutes": 30,
  "custom_shortcode": "abcd1"
}
